Suggests: protonmail-bridge
Description: Proton services integration for GNOME Online Accounts
 Integrates Proton Mail, Proton Drive, and Proton Calendar into
 GNOME Online Accounts, providing the same seamless experience as
 Google or Microsoft 365 accounts in GNOME.
 .
 After installation, add your Proton account in GNOME Settings,
 Online Accounts. This will automatically configure:
  - Mail (Geary/Evolution) via Proton Mail Bridge
  - Files/Drive (Nautilus sidebar) via rclone FUSE mount
  - Calendar (GNOME Calendar) via CalDAV bridge
